data.description: PRICE REDUCTION - Back on The Market- NO FAULT OF THE HOME, BUYER DID NOT PERFORM!!  Welcome to 1936 Tangelo Way, where you can experience the perfect blend of comfort and elegance in this stunning residence situated in the coveted Harvest Limoniera Community. This stunning model home features 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, an impressive loft and a spacious 1,870 square feet of living space. With $60,000 in meticulous upgrades throughout, this home truly captures luxurious comfort. The heart of the home boasts granite counters that extend throughout, enhancing both style and functionality. Nestled on a corner lot, this residence not only offers space, but also boasts spectacular views of the picturesque Santa Paula rolling hills. If that isn't enough let's talk about convenience which is paramount, and this home delivers! Strategically located near freeways and shopping, you'll find everything you need within easy reach. Whether you are commuting to work, or exploring all that Ventura County has to offer, you will find that living in the Harvest Limoniera Community puts it all at your fingertips. If you don't want to leave the comfort of the community then enjoy all the great amenities it has to offer, including a playground, gym, parks,  and gorgeous pool. Call to set up your private tour today.
